OL,3,CCouncillors declare vote of no
OL,4,Cconfidence in water company
OL,6,FCornwall councillors have declared a
OL,7,Fvote of no confidence in South West
OL,8,FWater stating the company has failed
OL,9,Fto manage the sewage system.
OL,11,FThey're also calling on the government
OL,12,Fand OFWAT to remove the water company
OL,13,Ffrom the management of the Cornish
OL,14,Fwater and wastewater systems and
OL,15,Ftransfer the ownership to a publicly
OL,16,Fowned organisation.
OL,18,FThey say that despite record bills and
OL,19,Fgovernment intervention, raw sewage
OL,20,Fcontinues to impact Cornwall's
OL,21,Fenvironment and public health.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
