OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784729924
OL,3,CCouncillors declare vote of no
OL,4,Cconfidence in water company
OL,6,FIt was put forward for debate by Cllr
OL,7,FLoveday Jenkin, and was seconded by
OL,8,FCllr Dean Evans, and drew support from
OL,9,Fall sides of the chamber.
OL,11,FIt followed similar votes of no
OL,12,Fconfidence from 16 town and parish
OL,13,Fcouncils in Cornwall in recent months.
OL,15,FCllr Jenkin introduced the debate,
OL,16,Fstating that it was not a criticism of
OL,17,Fthose working for South West Water in
OL,18,FCornwall, but focused on the senior
OL,19,Fmanagement and infrastructure of the
OL,20,Fbusiness.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784729924
OL,3,CCouncillors declare vote of no
OL,4,Cconfidence in water company
OL,6,FThe call for renationalisation of the
OL,7,Fwater company proved the only bone of
OL,8,Fcontention for some members, with some
OL,9,Fmembers stating they were unable to
OL,10,Fsupport the motion due to its
OL,11,Finclusion in the wording.
OL,13,FThe motion was supported with 68 votes
OL,14,Ffor and two abstentions.
OL,16,FSpeaking after the debate, Cllr Leigh
OL,17,FFrost, leader of Cornwall Council,
OL,18,Fsaid: "One of the key roles for this
OL,19,Fcouncil is to amplify the voice of our
OL,20,Fresidents and I am delighted we are
OL,21,Fstanding up and saying enough is eough.
OL,26,@zD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
