FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784729924
OL,3,CCouncillors declare vote of no
OL,4,Cconfidence in water company
OL,6,F"Despite so many promises, including
OL,7,Fafter a motion I raised myself in the
OL,8,Fchamber several years ago, nothing has
OL,9,Fhappened. I hope that, by speaking
OL,10,Fwith such a unified voice, the
OL,11,Ffrustrations of our communities are
OL,12,Fclear to the Government and we can
OL,13,Ffinally see some real change."
OL,15,FMotions calling for National Highways
OL,16,Fto review the safety of the A30 at
OL,17,FConnor Downs, for SEND reform through
OL,18,Ffairer funding, and one calling for
OL,19,Fthe Government to give council the
OL,20,Ftools to build homes, were also
OL,21,Fapproved by members.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@^O]
