OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784729924
OL,3,CCouncillors declare vote of no
OL,4,Cconfidence in water company
OL,6,FSouth West Water say they recognise
OL,7,Fthe concerns and are proactively
OL,8,Fworking with councils to explain local
OL,9,Fplans and deliver improvements.
OL,11,F"We're investing #760 million to
OL,12,Ftackle storm overflows and have
OL,13,Freduced spills by 17% in last year,
OL,14,Fwith spill duration down by 25%. We
OL,15,Fknow there is more to do, but the data
OL,16,Fshows the plan is working."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
